2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* NEWS, web/edit_entry.php, web/lang.en, web/view_entry.php
	  (mrbs-1_2-branch.[8,8,4,2]) (utags: mrbs-1_2_6): * Added copy
	  booking/series feature, as provided by Julian Eglestaff.   Adds
	  two new translation tokens, which are now only available in
	  English.

2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* NEWS (mrbs-1_2-branch.7): * Updated NEWS for release of 1.2.6.

2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/lang.fr (tags: mrbs-1_2_6) (mrbs-1_2-branch.2): * Removed a
	  few terminating colons in the French translation that  slipped
	  through. Gives me a chance to acknowledge dionysos-sf for
	  providing the updated French translation (in SF #1791821).

2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/: admin.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), auth_imap_php.inc (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), config.inc.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), day.php (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), edit_area_room.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6),
	  edit_entry.php, edit_entry_handler.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6),
	  functions.inc (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), functions_mail.inc (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.ca (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.cs (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.cz (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.da (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.de (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.el (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.en, lang.es (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.fi (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.fr, lang.it (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.ja (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.ko (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.nl (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.no (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.pt (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.sl (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.sv (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), lang.tr (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), lang.zh-tw (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), language.inc (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), month.php (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), mrbs_sql.inc (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), report.php (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), search.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), version.inc (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), view_entry.php, week.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6)
	  (mrbs-1_2-branch.[2,1,13,4,3,7,6,6,7,2,2,1,1,1,1,3,3,3,1,2,2,2,2,2,1,2,4,1,3,7,6,4,4,1,4,1,3]):
	  * Removed all terminating colons from the translations, moving
	  them to  the (arguably) correct place: the code.

	  * Added JavaScript and server side checking for setting of a
	  repeat day  if a booking requires one.

	  * Added server side checking for setting a valid n-weekly value.

	  * Emails sent by MRBS are now in UTF-8 (if $unicode_encoding is
	  1),  unless $mail_vocab is set to something else.

	  * Added Turkish support and translation, thanks to Ahmet YILDIZ.

	  * Removed possible infinite loop in n-weekly booking creation.

	  * Fixed invalid truncation of text in month.php, it could
	  truncate  descriptions mid-UTF8 sequence before.

	  * Added new auth method, imap_php, which authenticates via IMAP,
	  but  using the PHP 'imap' extension, which allows for SSL/TLS
	  connections.

	  * Upped version number to 1.2.6 in preparation for a release.

2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/auth_ldap.inc (tags: mrbs-1_2_6) (mrbs-1_2-branch.6): *
	  auth_ldap: Added support for searching the LDAP directory for the
	  full	DN to try and bind with. This allows for operation with
	  Microsoft AD	servers. Utilises new config variable
	  $ldap_dn_search_attrib, and  optionally $ldap_dn_search_dn (the
	  DN to bind with for the search) and  $ldap_dn_search_password
	  (the password to bind with). If $ldap_dn_search_dn  is set,
	  $ldap_dn_search_password MUST be set. NOTE: This is as yet
	  untested, as I don't currently have an MRBS test installation
	  that	can bind to an AD server for testing.

2008-01-28  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/auth_ldap.inc (mrbs-1_2-branch.5): * Detabbified (4 space
	  indent now) auth_ldap.inc, so it's easier to edit.   Only
	  whitespace changes.,

2007-09-07  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/edit_entry.php (mrbs-1_2-branch.6): * Fix for SF tracker
	  #1666299, as supplied by the reporter, 'northtommy'.	 Update of
	  the room list as you change area in the edit entry screen   is
	  now correct.

2007-06-18  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/edit_entry.php (mrbs-1_2-branch.5): * Fixed HTML escaping
	  problem in edit_entry.php, the ENT_NOQUOTES  mode of
	  htmlspecialchars() was being used, when it shouldn't have  been.

2007-06-18  John Beranek <jberanek@users.sourceforge.net>

	* checklang.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), web/edit_area_room.php,
	  web/edit_users.php (tags: mrbs-1_2_6), web/lang.ca,
	  web/language.inc, web/month.php, web/mysqli.inc (tags:
	  mrbs-1_2_6), web/pgsql.inc (tags: mrbs-1_2_6)
	  (mrbs-1_2-branch.[3,2,4,1,6,5,3,1]): * A few fixes in
	  checklang.php to make it work better and be more  useful.

	  * Removed unnecessary table HTML tags in edit_area_room.php.
	  Fixes SF tracker #1696383, as reported by 'mikedip'.

	  * Fixed SQL escaping in edit_users.php, also required changes  to
	  pgsql.inc and mysqli.inc to fix the sql_field_type() function.

	  * i18n/l10n fixes in language.inc. Windows locale map
	  extended/fixed,  added Catalan support, improved the map the Unix
	  locale map was  applied. Catalan translation provided by Jordi
	  Prats.

	  * Fixed bug in language preference code, fix supplied by
	  'mikedip'  in SF tracker #1696382.

