	* web/lang.zh-tw (tags: mrbs-1_2_3, mrbs-1_2_2)
	  (mrbs-1_2-branch.1): * Updated Taiwanese translation. Now stored
	  in UTF-8 encoding. Taiwanese	users who have set
	  $unicode_encoding to 0 will need to convert their  databases to
	  UTF-8.

