	* web/edit_users.php (1.4): The last change, to restrict access to
	  the page to identified users, broke the ability to initially
	  enter the first user! Fixed this by avoiding to do this test if
	  the user list is empty. Actually moved the code to a branch that
	  already ran only if the user list was not empty.

