2003-10-10  Thierry Bothorel <thierry_bo@users.sourceforge.net>

	* web/language.inc (1.2): - Changed getenv('HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE')
	  to $HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE.  getenv() does not work in ISAPI mode,
	  so getenv('HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE') is always NULL with ISAPI.
	  Global variable seems more reliable.

